20. Conclusion

The Credit Card Fraud Detection System demonstrates how Machine Learning and Data Analytics can improve financial transaction security.

The project successfully identifies fraudulent transactions using predictive modeling and classification algorithms. By automating fraud detection, the system reduces manual effort, minimizes financial losses, and enhances trust in digital banking systems.

This project can be further improved using advanced AI techniques, large-scale datasets, and real-time deployment infrastructure.

